  "title": "Invocation for when you find something becoming difficult for you",
  "source": "Hisn al-Muslim 139",
  "arabic": "اللَّهُمَّ لاَ سَهْلَ إِلاَّ مَا جَعَلْتَهُ سَهْلاً وَأَنْتَ تَجْعَلُ الْحَزْنَ إِذَا شِئْتَ سَهْلاً",
  "meaning": "O Allah, there is no ease except in that which You have made easy, and You make the difficulty, if You wish, easy.",
